# auto re-tile icons when list changes
AddToFunc TileIcons
 + C Iconify off
 + C All (CurrentPage, Iconic) PlaceAgain Icon

AddToFunc Move-or-Raise     "M" Raise
+                           "M" Move
+                           "D" Lower

AddToFunc Resize-or-Raise   "M" Raise
+                           "M" Resize
+                           "D" Lower

# double click max, single click move
AddToFunc Maximize-or-Move
 + D Maximize
 + I Raise
 + C Focus
 + M Move

